    LocDescriptions:
    - _name: FR
      Language: 0
      Txt: "Utilisez 1PA pour cibler une unit\xE9 visible, m\xEAme hors de port\xE9e,
        ne poss\xE9dant aucun marqueur \xAB cible \xBB et lancer 2D. L\u2019unit\xE9
        cibl\xE9e re\xE7oit ensuite 1 marqueur \xAB cible \xBB pour chaque r\xE9ussite
        obtenue."
    - _name: EN
      Language: 1
      Txt: "You may use 1AP to target a unit in line of sight, even out of range,
        if it doesn't have any \xAB target \xBB token. If you do, roll 2 dice. The
        targeted unit then receive a \xAB target \xBB token for each success result
        you get.\nWhen a unit attacks a unit with a \xAB target \xBB token, "
    ExportString: ':purple_square:'
